{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"22247-ape-and-crocodile","title":"Ape and Crocodile","description":"Do the Ape and the Crocodile have a happy friendship story? ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mulualem Daba"],"illustrators":["Abraham Muzee"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/22247-ape-and-crocodile"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130933/size3/94684613766dee09332eba2857f49e9b.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130933/size6/94684613766dee09332eba2857f49e9b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128943/size6/9127b41d835a908628913be4a343e9bf.jpg","text":"Ape meets Crocodile by the lake.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128944/size6/6a8420f04d7cba8a9f4b6aaad8a6dd7a.jpg","text":"“Where do you live?” asks Ape.\n“In the \nlake,” says Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128946/size6/30f582dfb8154af7d8aef6b9622e0b18.jpg","text":"“Where do you live?” asks Crocodile. \n“In the trees,”\nsays Ape.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128948/size6/0ba1353f30edfb15718a0843f424adc9.jpg","text":"“Can you swim?” \nasks Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128949/size6/7e5bf5576f54e0edaab3a9af5b820a29.jpg","text":"“I cannot swim,” says Ape. \n“I can teach you.”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128951/size6/fa99f2c1819415f62ae8fd81a30a19a2.jpg","text":"“We are friends. Do not be afraid,” says Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128956/size6/438ffbbb59de882f937e4a56eaaf6398.jpg","text":"“Ape, my uncle is sick. He needs meat,” says Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128960/size6/9faac76e7e8232b6e842cd97de25bc0c.jpg","text":"Ape is very afraid.\nWill Crocodile eat her?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128962/size6/ade52cc5479a0a2de3376d29ada2e13e.jpg","text":"Ape wants to escape from Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128964/size6/1d33c83a83af05a90c19120daf14d089.jpg","text":"Ape has an idea.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128965/size6/3025f20b829b9b343274686bbeab94a5.jpg","text":"“I will give you my heart for him,” Ape promises.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128967/size6/8778e6d6e3f1ce0481cc7f83ee1dcecc.jpg","text":"“My heart is in a tree on the land,” says Ape.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128968/size6/2a9c36bbd4a2d51e825ea69a71b399d9.jpg","text":"“Will you fetch your heart?” asks Crocodile. “Yes,” says Ape.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128970/size6/199064dbef69a3d993de1d50383effea.jpg","text":"Crocodile swims back to the land. Ape runs to the trees.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128972/size6/67f2317dd9bd1b8e072fb711a2e89ff6.jpg","text":"“You are not my friend. You lied!” says Crocodile.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128974/size6/bc60af238f2e2a589a04c62f2b994439.jpg","text":"“We are not friends. \nYou want to eat me!” says Ape.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":141}}